      "body" : "The QT behavior on mac will place menu action with string matching to \"config, options, setup, settings or preferences\" to the general application menu (at very left) and remove them from other menu positions (which is somehow weak IMO).\r\n\r\nCurrently i only added the `QAction::NoRole` role to the `showHelpMessageAction` action. It is might be discussable to add the \"NoRole\" to every \"standard menu action\".",
